Author: edthrowaway97
Text: Yeah. I feel like I would be a lot further ahead in life and a lot more successful at least academically if I didn't have to put up with this stupid bullshit. I wish I could just be normal.

Author: everythingabove02
Text: I'm so sorry to hear about your loss. I really hope, you will one day take it all back from your ED and get back on track  I know your feeling very too well. My ED has taken away the best years of my youth (16 until now, age 21). Actually it has totally taken away who I am. Jeez
